function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)
	
	local tGuards = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("Quest_Scos_Estate_Guards")
	
	-- Tether remaining guards to new position when exterior goatman are all dead
	for i, idActor in pairs(tGuards) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActor) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActor) then
			local idTether = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActor, "tether")[1]
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActor, idTether, "npc_run", true)
		end
	end	
	
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Boss_FirebreakFight_Victory")
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDonan, idMarkerDonan, "npc_run", true)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idDonan)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idDonan)
	Hydra.ActorSetSheathPreference(idDonan, 1)

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
		
	--Play Boss Music
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Boss_FirebreakFight_Phase1")
	
	
	idDonan = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "donan")[1]
	idMarkerDonan = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "marker_donan")[1]
	idInteriorMelee = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "pk_guard")[1]
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idInteriorMelee) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idInteriorMelee) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_ESTATE_ATTACK, idInteriorMelee)
	end
end
